                             Staufer V2.4



An accident in space and time structure changed the hististory of central
Europe since the year 1000 ac. The real sovereigns are replaced by
war-minded babariens, which can`t think of anything than making war with
their neighbours if they think they could win it. You are now playing the
role of a monach who managed to regain the power in his land and have to try
to beware your kingdom from decline and archive great power in Europe. But
be warned! If you grow to big, the other kingdoms will be afraid of you and
begin war together, until you are eliminatet or small enough. You also can
make allies with the other kingdoms and if they accept them, they won`t be
at war with you until they think they could win it or you are too powerful.
You also can invest your money in economy to produce better weapons and
armory.


Taking control of the game:

Most of the game is controlled by the menu. You have three main parts with
following sub parts to choose from.
-Disk
  -Load
    Click on the name of your saved game with the mouse pointer and contine
    with clicking "OK". Now the saved game will be loaded and continued,
    where it was saved.
  -Save
    Enter the name of your saved game or click on an already existing one to
    overwrite it. Now click "OK" and your game will be saved.
  -Quit
    To end the game and save the archived points, choose "Quit" and continue
    with "y". If you have accidently choosen "Quit" you can return to the
    game with "n". Now the ranks and the points of the kingdoms are shown.
    Press any key to go to the all time highscores of the kingdoms.
-Actions
  -Army
    If you choose "Army" then first time in your move your existing armies
    are shown one by one and you go to the armymenu. Through pressing "f",
    "m" and "d" you can choose from the following actions.
    -"f"ight  : The army moves on an area and conquers it. If you are allied
                with this kingdom the ally is broken and you are at war.
    -"m"ove   : The army moves on an area without conquering it. This is only
                possible if this is your area, water or if you are allied
                with this kingdom.
                In both moves "fight" and "move" all armies from kingdoms you
                are not allied with are attacked.
    -"d"isband: The army is disbanded and all soldiers return to the
                population.
    But if you choose "Army" the second time or if you have no armies, you
    move into the buildmenu where you can build new armies. There you are
    asked if you want another army. To build another army press the "y" key
    and enter the number of soldiers you want. Each soldier costs 1 kg
    silver per round. The click on the area where you want this army to be
    in. You can control up to 10 armies at the same time. To exit the
    buildmenu before you have 10 armies you have to press "n" in stead of
    "y".
  -Economy
    in the economymenu you can choose from following actions by entering
    their initial letter.
    -"T"axrate:The old taxrate is shown and you can enter a new taxrate. But
               don`t set the taxrate too high if you want to have enough
               people left.
    -"I"nvest :Enter the amount of money you want to invest. If you try to
               invest more than you have the amount will automatically be
               reduced to what you can effort. If you have invested enough
               your technologie level will increase by 1.
    -"E"xit   :Select "Exit" to leave the economymenu and return to the main
               menu.
  -Alliances
    Click on the kingdom with which you want to be allied and you will get a
    message if you where succesfull. If the other kingdom has a human player
    he is asked if he accepts the alliance. You are also asked during the
    turns of the computer players if you want an alliance. The color of the
    asker is shown in the text "Do you accept the alliance" and the color of
    the asked is shown in the text "(y/n) ?".
  -Next
    If you select this your turn is over and the next player can act.
-Speed
  In this menu you can alter the speed of the fights. But this doesn`t alter
  the fight itself.
  -faster
  -fast
  -normal
  -slow
  -key
    After each fightrund the computer waits for a keypress. (Only for very
    patient players.)


End of the game:

In the end of the year 1100 or if someone conquered everything, the game ends
automatically. But you can end the game everytime by choosing "Quit" from
the Diskmenu. Then the scores of the players are shown like they are
descibed at "-Quit".


